                  "format": 0,
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "style": "",
                  "text": "I've been wanting to include interactive code examples in the documentation for Dossier for a while now. I really enjoyed using Observable notebooks, but want something more integrated for the documentation. In addition, the fact that Observable is reactive requires a bit of a mental shift for the reader. A much simpler alternative is ",
                  "type": "text",
                  "version": 1
                },
