                  "text": ", which is now integrated into the Dossier documentation.",
                  "type": "text",
                  "version": 1
                },
                {
                  "type": "linebreak",
                  "version": 1
                },
                {
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "style": "",
                  "text": "Getting Dossier to run in codapi was straightforward, since Dossier can already run entirely in the browser. In order to get a simple code editor with syntax highlighting, I'm using ",
                  "type": "text",
                  "version": 1
                },
                {
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "detail": 0,
                      "format": 0,
                      "mode": "normal",
